oakcurric:unit-2890
  a curric:Unit ;
  rdfs:label "Travel and tourism: Révisions: Personnes et lieux"@en ;
  curric:slug "communication-and-the-world-around-us-revisions-personnes-et-lieux" ;
  rdfs:comment """This unit consolidates revision of vocabulary and grammar with a focus on
  negation, imperatives, present participles, adjective agreement and adjective and adverb
  positioning. In addition it revisits all word pattern rules met throughout the course."""@en ;
  curric:whyThisWhyNow """This unit allows pupils to apply their vocabulary and grammar knowledge in
  order to learn about the lives of famous French speakers and to enjoy a cultural exploration
  of Brussels. Negation and adjectival agreement and positioning are revisited along with word
  pattern rules, as pupils build greater confidence in applying these rules more accurately.""" ;
  curric:hasPriorKnowledgeRequirement
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2890-1 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2890-2 ,
    oakcurric:priorknowledge-2890-3 ,
